    "content": "<div class=\"noinclude\"><span class=\"breadcrumbs xulRefAttr_breadcrumbs\">Â« <a href=\"/en-US/docs/XUL/XUL_Reference\">XUL Reference home</a></span></div>\n\n<dl>\n <dt><code id=\"a-persistence\"><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL/Attribute/persistence\">persistence</a></code></dt>\n <dd>Type: <em>integer</em></dd>\n <dd>The persistence may be set to a non-zero value so that the <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL/notificationbox\" title=\"notificationbox\">notificationbox</a></code>'s <span id=\"m-removeTransientNotifications\"><code><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL/Method/removeTransientNotifications\">removeTransientNotifications</a></code></span> method does not remove them. This may be used to close a set of notifications as a group without affecting other notifications.</dd>\n</dl>",
